{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"418891-ajj-main-haan","title":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਹਾਂ","description":"ਅੱਜ ਮੇਘਾ ਕੀ ਬਣੇਗੀ? ਇੱਕ ਖੋਜਕਰਤਾ, ਇੱਕ ਪੁਲਾੜ ਯਾਤਰੀ ਜਾਂ ਫਿਰ ਇੱਕ ਚਿੱਤਰਕਾਰ?","language":"Punjabi","langCode":"pa","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Amandeep Kaur"],"illustrators":["Sandhya Prabhat"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/418891-ajj-main-haan"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/524542/size3/c273da52c55bd7e5d79cd98401ab3ab2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/524542/size6/c273da52c55bd7e5d79cd98401ab3ab2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79839/size6/1851e5b94ad11e38a3b2cde61db55123.jpg","text":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਇੱਕ ਪੁਲਾੜ ਯਾਤਰੀ ਹਾਂ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79842/size6/ec46fba085b7c0b7520393b6e2ac5595.jpg","text":"ਦੇਖੋ-ਦੇਖੋ ਮੈਂ ਚੰਨ ’ਤੇ ਕਿੰਨੀ ਵੱਡੀ ਛਾਲ਼ ਮਾਰ ਸਕਦੀ ਹਾਂ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79846/size6/064618d423802e81431a50ec9c574156.jpg","text":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਹਾਂ, ਇੱਕ ਮੂਰਤੀਕਾਰ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79848/size6/9027bf58d6fde98a2bbcd06b7956240d.jpg","text":"ਦੇਖਿਓ ਸੰਭਲ਼ਕੇ! ਮੇਰੇ ਮਗਰਮੱਛ ਅਤੇ ਡਾਇਨਾਸੋਰ ਭੁੱਖੇ ਹਨ। ਗਰਰਰ..","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79849/size6/bf9cc0b14bae2957869e160f1f35a525.jpg","text":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਇੱਕ ਕ੍ਰਿਕਟ ਖਿਡਾਰੀ ਹਾਂ।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79850/size6/c177b8f8619d94ff6120879fcd3645a2.jpg","text":"ਹੁਣ ਗੇਂਦਬਾਜੀ ਦੀ ਵਾਰੀ ਹੈ ਮੇਰੀ।\nਆਹ ਲਓ... ਤੁਸੀਂ ਆਊਟ ਹੋ ਗਏ।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79851/size6/f8f6ce4db1412cc86f58c0f3f83a1592.jpg","text":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਹਾਂ, ਇੱਕ ਬਨਸਪਤੀ ਵਿਗਿਆਨੀ।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/80013/size6/38eddd9f67af4042a5c6c59f27ccca51.jpg","text":"ਮੈਂ ਇੱਕ ਨਵੇਂ ਬੂਟੇ ਦੀ ਖੋਜ ਕੀਤੀ ਹੈ। ਮੈਂ ਆਪਣੇ ਨਾਂ ’ਤੇ ਇਸਦਾ ਨਾਂ ਰੱਖਾਂਗੀ।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79853/size6/c60ae14f325211467333dd90f2dc3d5e.jpg","text":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਹਾਂ ਇੱਕ ਡਰੱਮ ਵਜਾਉਣ ਵਾਲ਼ੀ।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79854/size6/90ef5f7c7a184ec7371c2c1a6d410830.jpg","text":"ਡੁਸ਼ਅਅ...ਟਸ਼ਅਅ....! ਮੇਰੇ ਡਰੱਮ ਦੀਆਂ ਡੰਡੀਆਂ ਐਨੀ ਤੇਜ਼ੀ ਨਾਲ਼ ਚੱਲ ਰਹੀਆਂ ਹਨ ਕਿ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਦੇਖ ਵੀ ਨਹੀਂ ਸਕਦੇ।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79855/size6/0296786590d7aa884ec45c3905f0245b.jpg","text":"ਅੱਜ ਮੈਂ ਕਿੰਨਾ ਕੁਝ ਬਣੀ।\nਹੁਣ ਕੱਲ ਮੈਂ ਕੀ ਬਣਾਂਗੀ?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":105}}